# Department Domain Standards

This profile requires the dependencies declared in `.governance-profile.json`.
Apply them before this profile. Read each owned rule in `references/rules/`
before changing code in its scope.

Document every parent-rule replacement explicitly, including the reason,
owner, validation command, and expiration date if it is temporary. Do not
apply this profile outside a repository that declares it in
`.claude/governance.json`.
